Localization.Name: Greycat Industrial
Localization.Description: A trusted manufacturer of industrial tools since 2337, the company’s extensive line of industrial equipment and armor make it one of the most respected brand names around. Greycat has remained a UEE staple for centuries thanks to their streamlined-yet-inventive designs, exacting safety standards, and a diverse product line.

Localization.Name: Aril Arms Scorched
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Medium Armor
Damage Reduction: 30%
Temp. Rating: -61 / 91 °C
Radiation Protection: 26400 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 145.8 REM/s
 
Originally designed for miners, the Aril armor includes a fully enclosed helmet and high collar providing additional support and protection for the neck and back of the head. An integrated tool belt and attachable backpack can accommodate a variety of tools and supplies to keep your hands free. The Aril armor is available in a variety of vibrant colors to fit your personal taste and for easy identification on the jobsite.

Localization.Name: Virgil
Localization.Description:
High-end Commercial and Personal armor manufacturer. Aside from combat uses, they build systems for heavy commercial and mining applications.

Models: Achilles PDS (Heavy Combat Armor)

Zeus System (Titan Armor)

Localization.Name: TruDef-Pro Legs Scorched
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Light Armor
Damage Reduction: 20%
Temp. Rating: -38 / 68 °C
Radiation Protection: 26000 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 145.8 REM/s
Carrying Capacity: 2.0 µSCU

Virgil's TrueDef line of personal body armor provide strategic protection of vital areas while keeping you fast and mobile. Numerous planetary law enforcement organizations and even the Advocacy use versions of the TrueDef to protect their officers and agents."
